description:
7/7 Ten Years On PDTV x264-TASTETV

Hard to believe it's ten years since the London bombings, when a series of suicide attacks killed 52 people using public transport during the morning rush hour, just one day after the Olympic games were awarded to London. This documentary hears stories from those bereaved as well as stories of bravery in the aftermath of what became knows as 7/7.
